ription\":\"Fushi is an immortal being that can take the form of anything that has given him stimuli.\",\"Description_2\":\"His original form was a featureless white sphere. Without consciousness, he copied the first thing he bumped into, which happened to be a rock. Soon afterward, he became moss and stayed like that for some time. When a wounded wolf wandered close in the middle of winter and died, the immortal copied the wolf. He retains the ability to turn into these things.\",\"Description_3\":\"Later, after the death of The Nameless Boy, he mimicked the boy\\u0027s appearance and took the form of a young boy with white hair, pale complexion, and green eyes. He wears a short, brown fur cloak and a light blue shirt and pants with fur boots. A rope dangled from his hand and neck as The Nameless Boy died holding Joaan\\u0027s leash, though the latter soon disappeared. The injury that took The Boy\\u0027s life is also present on Fushi\\u0027s left leg. Fushi commented that this form felt like it belonged to him the most.\",\"(Source\":\"To Your Eternity Wiki, edited)\"}','{\"Age\": \"~800 years (according to books about him)\", \"Sex\": \"male (in his main form); can be female\", \"(Source\": \"To Your Eternity Wiki, edited)\", \"Species\": \"Immortal\", \"Relatives\": \"The Beholder (\\\"father,\\\" creator); March (adoptive \\\"mother\\\"); Gugu (adoptive brother)\", \"Affiliation\": \"The Guardian Force (formerly); Tonari\'s Group (formerly); Booze Man\'s Shop (formerly); Aoki Family (currently)\", \"Description\": \"Fushi is an immortal being that can take the form of anything that has given him stimuli.\", \"Description_2\": \"His original form was a featureless white sphere. Without consciousness, he copied the first thing he bumped into, which happened to be a rock. Soon afterward, he became moss and stayed like that for some time. When a wounded wolf wandered close in the middle of winter and died, the immortal copied the wolf. He retains the ability to turn into these things.\", \"Description_3\": \"Later, after the death of The Nameless Boy, he mimicked the boy\'s appearance and took the form of a young boy with white hair, pale complexion, and green eyes. He wears a short, brown fur cloak and a light blue shirt and pants with fur boots. A rope dangled from his hand and neck as The Nameless Boy died holding Joaan\'s leash, though the latter soon disappeared. The injury that took The Boy\'s life is also present on Fushi\'s left leg. Fushi commented that this form felt like it belonged to him the most.\"}'),(833,151351,'Booze Man','{}','{}'),(834,151297,'Chan','{\"Description\":\"His father is a kind farmer who hires Gugu even after Gugu\\u0027s face gets mutilated. He tells Gugu to stop coming to work because Gugu is causing trouble for his father.\"}','{\"Description\": \"His father is a kind farmer who hires Gugu even after Gugu\'s face gets mutilated. He tells Gugu to stop coming to work because Gugu is causing trouble for his father.\"}'),(835,201401,'Chan\'s Father','{}','{}'),(836,151298,'Cropp, Rean','{\"Description\":\"Rean is a young girl around 13 years old. She has long blond hair and purple eyes. She is outgoing, rebellious, and prefers to live life freely. She dislikes how her parents treat her and feels they haven\\u0027t recognized her as an individual.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Rean is a young girl around 13 years old. She has long blond hair and purple eyes. She is outgoing, rebellious, and prefers to live life freely. She dislikes how her parents treat her and feels they haven\'t recognized her as an individual.\"}'),(837,153666,'Dalton, Tonari','{\"Age\":\"14\",\"Relatives\":\"Unnamed Mother; Erran G. Dalton (Father)\",\"Affiliation\":\"Tonari\\u0027s Group (formerly)\",\"Residence\":\"Jananda\",\"Description\":\"Tonari is a young girl about 14 years old. She has short brown hair, green eyes, and tan skin. She wears a light blue jacket and shorts, a black and white shirt, and is often seen with her pet owl, Ricard. She also has a triangle carved in the palm of her right hand. Tonari is clever, cunning, and appears to be a bit manipulative. She has a great love for reading and writing and she cares greatly for her friends.\"}','{\"Age\": \"14\", \"Relatives\": \"Unnamed Mother; Erran G. Dalton (Father)\", \"Residence\": \"Jananda\", \"Affiliation\": \"Tonari\'s Group (formerly)\", \"Description\": \"Tonari is a young girl about 14 years old. She has short brown hair, green eyes, and tan skin. She wears a light blue jacket and shorts, a black and white shirt, and is often seen with her pet owl, Ricard. She also has a triangle carved in the palm of her right hand. Tonari is clever, cunning, and appears to be a bit manipulative. She has a great love for reading and writing and she cares greatly for her friends.\"}'),(838,153665,'Dalton, Erran G','{\"Description\":\"Tonari\\u0027s father.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Tonari\'s father.\"}'),(839,151296,'Gugu','{\"Description\":\"Gugu is a young boy from Takunaha who works at Booze Man\\u0027s shop.\",\"Description_2\":\"From a young age, Gugu and his brother, Shin, have been working as servants for various families. Because he was so young, Gugu mistook one employer as his family and was confused when they moved away but didn\\u0027t bring Shin and him along.\",\"Description_3\":\"A few years later, Shin and Gugu promised each other to work hard and earn money to build a big house.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Gugu is a young boy from Takunaha who works at Booze Man\'s shop.\", \"Description_2\": \"From a young age, Gugu and his brother, Shin, have been working as servants for various families. Because he was so young, Gugu mistook one employer as his family and was confused when they moved away but didn\'t bring Shin and him along.\", \"Description_3\": \"A few years later, Shin and Gugu promised each other to work hard and earn money to build a big house.\"}'),(840,151301,'Hayase','{\"Description\":\"A woman from the land of Yanome sent to oversee the yearly sacrifice of a young Ninannah girl to their god in exchange for safety. She is a recurring antagonist in the series.\"}','{\"Description\": \"A woman from the land of Yanome sent to oversee the yearly sacrifice of a young Ninannah girl to their god in exchange for safety. She is a recurring antagonist in the series.\"}'),(841,151306,'Joan','{\"Description\":\"The nameless boy\\u0027s wolf companion.\"}','{\"Description\": \"The nameless boy\'s wolf companion.\"}'),(842,169104,'Kansatsusha','{\"Description\":\"Fushi\\u0027s creator and the narrator of Fumetsu no Anata e.\",\"(Source\":\"Fumetsu no Anata e Fandom Wiki)\"}','{\"(Source\": \"Fumetsu no Anata e Fandom Wiki)\", \"Description\": \"Fushi\'s creator and the narrator of Fumetsu no Anata e.\"}'),(843,263751,'Lee','{}','{}'),(844,151295,'March','{\"Description\":\"One of the first humans Fushi meets in their travels. She is chosen by a fake village shaman to serve as sacrifice to Oniguma, the god that provides the Ninnanah tribe with prosperity.\"}','{\"Description\": \"One of the first humans Fushi meets in their travels. She is chosen by a fake village shaman to serve as sacrifice to Oniguma, the god that provides the Ninnanah tribe with prosperity.\"}'),(845,153962,'Mia','{\"Description\":\"Mia likes looking for curly hair.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Mia likes looking for curly hair.\"}'),(846,219561,'Nando','{}','{}'),(847,201342,'Oniguma','{}','{}'),(848,153964,'Oopa','{\"Description\":\"Oopa is a young girl from Jananda and a member of Tonari\\u0027s group.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Oopa is a young girl from Jananda and a member of Tonari\'s group.\"}'),(849,151300,'Parona','{\"Species\":\"Human\",\"Sex\":\"Female\",\"Age\":\"15\",\"Relatives\":\"Unnamed Sister; Unnamed Parents\",\"Residence\":\"Ninannah\",\"Description\":\"Parona is a young girl around the age of 15 and a close friend of March. She has long black hair that is tied in a loose ponytail. She wears a dress with cloth wrapped around her arms and legs. Parona is clever, observant, courageous, and selfless. She strongly opposes the Ninannah tradition of sacrificial ceremonies.\",\"(Source\":\"To Your Eternity Wiki)\"}','{\"Age\": \"15\", \"Sex\": \"Female\", \"(Source\": \"To Your Eternity Wiki)\", \"Species\": \"Human\", \"Relatives\": \"Unnamed Sister; Unnamed Parents\", \"Residence\": \"Ninannah\", \"Description\": \"Parona is a young girl around the age of 15 and a close friend of March. She has long black hair that is tied in a loose ponytail. She wears a dress with cloth wrapped around her arms and legs. Parona is clever, observant, courageous, and selfless. She strongly opposes the Ninannah tradition of sacrificial ceremonies.\"}'),(850,151299,'Pyoran','{\"Description\":\"Pyoran helps Fushi escape from where they were being kept as prisoners. She later also teaches him language, script, and how to live as a human.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Pyoran helps Fushi escape from where they were being kept as prisoners. She later also teaches him language, script, and how to live as a human.\"}'),(851,153963,'Sander','{\"Age\":\"11\"}','{\"Age\": \"11\"}'),(852,151368,'Shin','{\"Description\":\"Gugu\\u0027s older brother.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Gugu\'s older brother.\"}'),(853,153961,'Uroy','{\"Description\":\"Uroy is a boy from Jeannanda. His favorite food is chicken.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Uroy is a boy from Jeannanda. His favorite food is chicken.\"}'),(854,168013,'Alme','{\"Description\":\"The Princess of Renryrr who does not reveal her face generally.\"}','{\"Description\": \"The Princess of Renryrr who does not reveal her face generally.\"}'),(855,220856,'Anna','{}','{}'),(856,176202,'Ano','{\"Description\":\"Ano is Messar\\u0027s older half-brother.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Ano is Messar\'s older half-brother.\"}'),(857,167015,'Bastar, Messar Robin','{}','{}'),(858,168565,'Boldoron, King','{\"Description\":\"The King of Renryl.\",\"Description_2\":\"No voice actor