 Kingdom, as well as the mentor to Akira Oda. Being the one of the only ones to notice Akira\'s skill, he decides to take him under his wing.\"}'),(920,280477,'Nanase, Rintarou','{}','{}'),(921,280483,'Retice, Maria Rose','{}','{}'),(922,280482,'Retice, Edmond Rose','{}','{}'),(923,281379,'Rosequartz, Kilika','{}','{}'),(924,281874,'Rosequartz, Olive','{}','{}'),(925,280480,'Sano, Miko','{}','{}'),(926,201826,'Satou, Tsukasa','{\"Description\":\"Classmate that got summoned with Akira, with the title of Hero. While in the world prior to being isekai\\u0027d, Tsukasa felt resentment toward Akira for not acknowledging him, thus causing distance to grow between them.\"}','{\"Description\": \"Classmate that got summoned with Akira, with the title of Hero. While in the world prior to being isekai\'d, Tsukasa felt resentment toward Akira for not acknowledging him, thus causing distance to grow between them.\"}'),(927,281875,'Tres, Aurum','{}','{}'),(928,280478,'Tsuda, Tomoya','{}','{}'),(929,280476,'Ueno, Yuuki','{}','{}'),(930,280479,'Waki, Daisuke','{}','{}'),(931,192044,'Kohinata, Ozuma','{\"Description\":\"Ozuma is a second-year high school student. He is a typical \\u0022nice guy\\u0022 who is attentive and considerate. Ozuma is handsome like a prince and is actually a genius programmer.\",\"Description_2\":\"He is also Akiteru\\u0027s only friend and puts absolute trust in Akiteru due to certain events in the past.\",\"(Source\":\"GA Bunko, translated)\"}','{\"(Source\": \"GA Bunko, translated)\", \"Description\": \"Ozuma is a second-year high school student. He is a typical \\\"nice guy\\\" who is attentive and considerate. Ozuma is handsome like a prince and is actually a genius programmer.\", \"Description_2\": \"He is also Akiteru\'s only friend and puts absolute trust in Akiteru due to certain events in the past.\"}'),(932,180157,'Kohinata, Iroha','{\"Description\":\"Iroha is a first-year high school student. She is Akiteru\\u0027s best friend\\u0027s sister. She is a bright, kind, and beautiful honor student. However, she is easily excited and doesn\\u0027t know to how to read the atmosphere, as well as doing things in her own pace.\",\"Description_2\":\"Strangely, she is clingy towards Akiteru.\",\"(Source\":\"GA Bunko, translated)\"}','{\"(Source\": \"GA Bunko, translated)\", \"Description\": \"Iroha is a first-year high school student. She is Akiteru\'s best friend\'s sister. She is a bright, kind, and beautiful honor student. However, she is easily excited and doesn\'t know to how to read the atmosphere, as well as doing things in her own pace.\", \"Description_2\": \"Strangely, she is clingy towards Akiteru.\"}'),(933,192046,'Ooboshi, Akiteru','{\"Description\":\"Akiteru is a second-year high school student. He efficiently passes through his youth. He calls himself an average high school student in every aspect, but he has a hidden side to him.\",\"(Source\":\"GA Bunko, translated)\"}','{\"(Source\": \"GA Bunko, translated)\", \"Description\": \"Akiteru is a second-year high school student. He efficiently passes through his youth. He calls himself an average high school student in every aspect, but he has a hidden side to him.\"}'),(934,180154,'Tsukinomori, Mashiro','{\"Description\":\"Mashiro is a second-year high school student. She is Akiteru\\u0027s classmate and cousin. Mashiro is shy around strangers. However, she has a cold attitude and poisonous tongue only towards Akiteru.\",\"(Source\":\"GA Bunko, translated)\"}','{\"(Source\": \"GA Bunko, translated)\", \"Description\": \"Mashiro is a second-year high school student. She is Akiteru\'s classmate and cousin. Mashiro is shy around strangers. However, she has a cold attitude and poisonous tongue only towards Akiteru.\"}'),(935,244785,'Kageishi, Midori','{}','{}'),(936,192043,'Kageishi, Sumire','{\"Age\":\"25\",\"Description\":\"A teacher with a clear mind. She is Akiteru\\u0027s homeroom teacher and teacher with a ruthless guidance and a poisonous tongue.\",\"Description_2\":\"However, she has a side that no one knows...\",\"(Source\":\"GA Bunko, translated)\"}','{\"Age\": \"25\", \"(Source\": \"GA Bunko, translated)\", \"Description\": \"A teacher with a clear mind. She is Akiteru\'s homeroom teacher and teacher with a ruthless guidance and a poisonous tongue.\", \"Description_2\": \"However, she has a side that no one knows...\"}'),(937,280414,'Otoi','{}','{}'),(938,280415,'Suzuki, Takeshi','{}','{}'),(939,281735,'Tachibana, Asagi','{}','{}'),(940,283153,'Tomosaka, Sasara','{\"Description\":\"Sasara Tomosaka is a first year student at Kouzai High School. She is a good-looking girl who\\u0027s second in her year, as well as an influencer who boasts a million followers on Pinstagram.\",\"(Source\":\"Imouza Wiki)\"}','{\"(Source\": \"Imouza Wiki)\", \"Description\": \"Sasara Tomosaka is a first year student at Kouzai High School. She is a good-looking girl who\'s second in her year, as well as an influencer who boasts a million followers on Pinstagram.\"}'),(941,280404,'Tsukinomori, Makoto','{}','{}'),(942,173843,'Fel','{}','{}'),(943,173846,'Mukouda, Tsuyoshi','{}','{}'),(944,173845,'Sui','{\"Description\":\"A slime Mukouda befriended as his familiar due to its general cuteness and usefulness when cleaning his garbage from another world. It usually hangs inside of Mukouda\\u0027s bag, as a travel companion to him and Fel.\",\"Description_2\":\"Thought to be a regular water slime at first, Sui, thanks to Mukouda\\u0027s food providing ridiculous stat boosts, quickly learns how to use magic, how to speak, and how to produce high grade medicine.\",\"Description_3\":\"Sui is shown as being highly excitable and very supportive, extruding a positive attitude towards life, be it helping out its companions or killing powerful monsters.\",\"Description_4\":\"When Sui likes something, it creates a heart-shaped emote inside of it\\u0027s body.\"}','{\"Description\": \"A slime Mukouda befriended as his familiar due to its general cuteness and usefulness when cleaning his garbage from another world. It usually hangs inside of Mukouda\'s bag, as a travel companion to him and Fel.\", \"Description_2\": \"Thought to be a regular water slime at first, Sui, thanks to Mukouda\'s food providing ridiculous stat boosts, quickly learns how to use magic, how to speak, and how to produce high grade medicine.\", \"Description_3\": \"Sui is shown as being highly excitable and very supportive, extruding a positive attitude towards life, be it helping out its companions or killing powerful monsters.\", \"Description_4\": \"When Sui likes something, it creates a heart-shaped emote inside of it\'s body.\"}'),(945,222536,'Agni','{}','{}'),(946,225734,'Annette','{}','{}'),(947,282005,'Bookstore Owner','{}','{}'),(948,243262,'Butcher Shop Owner','{}','{}'),(949,282004,'Coachman','{}','{}'),(950,223877,'Edgar','{}','{}'),(951,243269,'Edmon','{}','{}'),(952,223547,'Franka','{}','{}'),(953,243270,'Griffon','{}','{}'),(954,225735,'Johan','{}','{}'),(955,282006,'Kiel\'s Adventurers Guild Receptionist','{}','{}'),(956,223555,'King','{}','{}'),(957,222537,'Kisharle','{}','{}'),(958,225326,'Lambert','{}','{}'),(959,225327,'Lars','{}','{}'),(960,226853,'Marie','{}','{}'),(961,282007,'Merchant','{}','{}'),(962,223878,'Michaela','{}','{}'),(963,173844,'Ninlil','{}','{}'),(964,223544,'Oono, Kanon','{}','{}'),(965,223556,'Princess','{}','{}'),(966,223550,'Ramon','{}','{}'),(967,223548,'Rita','{}','{}'),(968,282003,'Robert','{}','{}'),(969,222538,'Rusalka','{}','{}'),(970,223543,'Saitou, Kaito','{}','{}'),(971,224333,'Vianca','{}','{}'),(972,223549,'Vincent','{}','{}'),(973,223546,'Werner','{}','{}'),(974,226014,'Willem','{}','{}'),(975,223545,'Yoshida, Rio','{}','{}'),(976,270955,'Dora-chan','{}','{}'),(977,283284,'Adriano','{}','{}'),(978,282327,'Cyril','{}','{}'),(979,282787,'Daryl','{}','{}'),(980,277849,'Elrand','{}','{}'),(981,282330,'Francisca','{}','{}'),(982,277850,'Hephaestus','{}','{}'),(983,282788,'Iris','{}','{}'),(